trg_text: BillsCabinet approved the publication of the Victim Support Services Bill of 2019 for public commen The Bill provides for integrated and multi-disciplinary intervention approach towards the needs of victims of crime and violenc Through this bill the activities and services by various departments in the Justice, Crime Prevention and Security Cluster and the Social Cluster will be better coordinated as part of a singular value chai Cabinet also approved the Victim Support Services Policy 2019.Cabinet also approved the Social Services Practitioners Bill of 2019 to be gazetted for public commen The Bill was developed to expand the regulation of social service practitioners by recognising that there are both professional and auxiliary levels within the social service occupation This Bill once it is legislated, will repeal the current Social Service Professional Act, 1978 (Act 110 of 1978).

src_text: 2030)1 Khabinete yi hlamuseriwe hi vuenti hi mayelana na NSP 2020-2030 leyi nyikaka pholisi ya matirhelo ya tisekitaranyingi leri khomaneke na rimba ra nongonoko ku vona leswaku kun a ku angula eka GBV ka tiko hinkwaro loku hlanganisiweke hi mfumo na tiko hinkwar Khabinete yi pasise leswaku minongonoko hinkwayo leyi pfuniwaka hi timali ta kungu yi fanele ku tirhisiwa hi tindzawulo leti khumbekaka to hambanahambanaHambiswiritano, Khabinete yi lerise leswaku ku tirhisa ntirho wun wana eka ku olovisa matirhelo ya nhlangano lama ringanyetiweke na ku hlanganisiwa ka ntirho low Vaholobye lava landzelaka va lerisiwile ku endla ntirho wo tatisela hi mukhuva wolowo: Holobye wa Nhluvukiso wa Vaaki, Lindiwe Zulu; Holobye wa Vululami na Vukorhokeri bya Makhotso, Ronald Lamula; Holobye wa Maphorisa, Bheki Cele; Holobye wa Vaxisati, Vantshwa na Vatsoniwa, Nkoana-Mashabane va ta hlangana na ntlawa low Swibumabumelo swa Phanele yo Tsundzuxa leyi rhangeriweke hi Phuresidente hi mayelana na Antswiso wa Misava na Vurimi1 Hi siku ra 24 Mawuwani 2019, Khabinete yi amukele Xiviko xa Phanele yo Tsundzuxa leyi rhangeriweke hi Phuresidente hi mayelana na Antswiso wa Misava na Vurimi leyi a yi fambisiwa hi Dokodela Vuyokazi Mahlati leyi nga ta na swibumabumelo swa 73.

src_text: Hi ku tirhisa Komiti ya Tindzawulo to Hambana ya Antswiso wa Misava leyi a yi rhangeriwe hi Xandla xa Presidente, Mabuza, tindzawulo hinkwato leti khumbekaka ti komberiwile ku hlaya swibumabumelo leswi fambelanaka na tiphotifoliyo ta tona na ku angula hindlela leyi fanelekeKhabinete se yi amukerile na ku seketela 60 wa swibumabumelo lesw I kaye wa swona ntsena leswi nga pasisiwangiki, naswona swinharhu swi tekeriwile enhlokwen Tindzawulo to hambanahambana ti ta nyika vuxokoxoko hi vuenti eka swiyenge leswi tekeriweke enhlokweni naswona a swi nga pasisiwang Phurojeke yo Antswisa Magondzokulu ya le Gauteng (GFIP)1 Khabinete yi tekele enhlokweni xiviko xa GFIP (magondzo yo theleriwa) xa Xipano xa Ntirho lexi rhangeriweke hi Holobye wa swa Vutleketli, Fikile Mbalul Xiboho xo hetelela hi mayelana na swibumabumelo swa wona tanihilaha swi nga kona eka xiviko swi ta endliwa swi tiveka eka Lembe Lerintshw Pholisi ya ku Hlawuriwa ka Vavuyeriwa na Avelo wa Misava1 Khabinete yi pasise ku hangalasiwa ka pholisi leswaku vaaki va nyika mavonelo Pholisi yi lulamisela endlelo leri tshembekeke na ku va erivaleni eka avelo wa misava na ku hlawuriwa ka vavuyeriwaXa nkoka swinene, yi tirhana na ku pfumala ku ringana eka avelo na mfikelelo wa misava na ku pfumaleka ka tindlela to pfuneta vaaki lava nga evuswetini na vatshami va le migangeni ku fikelela misava loko ku tshuka ku va na timhangu ta ntumbuluko na swiyimo swa xilamulelamhangu swin wan Milawumbisi17.
